018package com.crossideas.ap.common.external.bean;
019
020import java.util.Date;
021
022import com.crossideas.ap.backend.util.enums.RequestStatus;
023import com.crossideas.ap.backend.util.enums.RequestType;
024import com.ibm.it.isig.Copyright;
025
026public class RequestDetail {
027
028        /** Copyright */
029        public static final String COPYRIGHT = Copyright.COPYRIGHT;
030
031        private Long parentId;
032        private Long requestId;
033        private RequestType requestType;
034        private RequestStatus requestStatus;
035        private Date createdOn;
036        private String note;
037        private String authorizationToken;
038
039        private String restURL;
040
041        public RequestDetail() {}
042        
043        public RequestDetail(String restUrl) {
044                this.restURL = restUrl;
045        }
046
047        public Long getParentId() {
048                return parentId;
049        }
050
051        public void setParentId(Long parentId) {
052                this.parentId = parentId;
053        }
054
055        public Long getRequestId() {
056                return requestId;
057        }
058
059        public void setRequestId(Long requestId) {
060                this.requestId = requestId;
061        }
062
063        public RequestType getRequestType() {
064                return requestType;
065        }
066
067        public void setRequestType(RequestType requestType) {
068                this.requestType = requestType;
069        }
070
071        public Date getCreatedOn() {
072                return createdOn;
073        }
074
075        public void setCreatedOn(Date createdOn) {
076                this.createdOn = createdOn;
077        }
078
079        public String getNote() {
080                return note;
081        }
082
083        public void setNote(String note) {
084                this.note = note;
085        }
086
087        public String getAuthorizationToken() {
088                return authorizationToken;
089        }
090
091        public void setAuthorizationToken(String authorizationToken) {
092                this.authorizationToken = authorizationToken;
093        }
094
095        public RequestStatus getRequestStatus() {
096                return requestStatus;
097        }
098
099        public void setRequestStatus(RequestStatus requestStatus) {
100                this.requestStatus = requestStatus;
101        }
102
103        @Override
104        public String toString() {
105                return "RequestDetail [parentId=" + parentId + ", requestId=" + requestId + ", requestType=" + requestType + ", requestStatus=" + requestStatus + ", createdOn=" + createdOn + ", note=" +
106                                note + ", authorizationToken=" + authorizationToken + "]";
107        }
108
109        public String getRestURL() {
110                return restURL;
111        }
112
113        public void setRestURL(String restURL) {
114                this.restURL = restURL;
115        }
116
117}
